txt.en: 'It is as I feared then. This was just a diversion!'
'Quickly, [placeholder], you must return to the cart.'
'I had finished stacking these goods when someone pushed me.'
'Who ever it was pushed the crates over, trying to topple them on me!'
'I did not see who it was. They vanished into the reeds so quickly.'
'I hope that we are not too late.'
